SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [RolePermissions] AS [r]
        WHERE [r].[RoleId] IN (
            SELECT [u].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__userRoleIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [u]
        ) AND [r].[PermissionId] = @__permission_Id_1) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
